{"tid":1359674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"良田村比人搶電話都冇人講？","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:41:40.000Z","uid":107060,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f216275bb63c10db4bf8810c2341d91f96ec9cee","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n<br />\n（12:00）【最緊要人無事】@屯門良田<br />\n<br />\n剛才屯門良田村，有一位黑衫街坊被幾個白衫人攻擊，期間差點被拖進村內，幸好及時有人出手幫助。該名街坊手腳擦傷，暫時安全，希望傷勢沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n但白衫人在捉人期間，曾經搶手機拍攝一些「溝通群組」，甚至想搶走電話，最終手機被毀爛後奪回。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有一些街坊均報稱收到「133」的匿名電話，亦有出言問候及套料等。<br />\n<br />\n大家千萬要注意個人安全，一定要避免落單工作，而曾進入一些地區群組，亦要注意小心個人資訊外洩，謹慎行事，平安順利。"},{"pid":"7784b7dbe84a492513f664e56abb0916ca237fad","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a9b60d377c9d01ebe9fa396ce8322d3a067ea6","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ed8762d76ecc81ae4d66814a9d9867d595780b","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561ccab33f3a9d49ea3aa5b4cc3d0a24a01f4681","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8415f4f797c43cbd4ce40098334438744d275f7","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad858722b6cdcf0a71c9250e0bf6acf92811e07","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39abcd763ce1fdb01c9ae013057072570e0c3fb9","tid":1359674,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f216275bb63c10db4bf8810c2341d91f96ec9cee","tid":1359674,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n<br />\n（12:00）【最緊要人無事】@屯門良田<br />\n<br />\n剛才屯門良田村，有一位黑衫街坊被幾個白衫人攻擊，期間差點被拖進村內，幸好及時有人出手幫助。該名街坊手腳擦傷，暫時安全，希望傷勢沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n但白衫人在捉人期間，曾經搶手機拍攝一些「溝通群組」，甚至想搶走電話，最終手機被毀爛後奪回。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有一些街坊均報稱收到「133」的匿名電話，亦有出言問候及套料等。<br />\n<br />\n大家千萬要注意個人安全，一定要避免落單工作，而曾進入一些地區群組，亦要注意小心個人資訊外洩，謹慎行事，平安順利。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"即晚有人講啦"}]}